					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6041369#post-3820638</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6041369/scp-3342#post-3820638</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 02 Jun 2018 00:12:39 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>TL333s</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1304786</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>So initially I was thinking, okay, this is different, not too amazing, it's probably still worth an upvote.</p> <p>Then the dude started carving organs out of potatoes and things got interesting.</p> <blockquote> <p>56 bullet wounds are found on the the body.</p> </blockquote> <p>This is where it went from &quot;more interesting than I anticipated&quot; to &quot;oh shit, son&quot;. That was well and truly terrifying, and a good reason why you don't use anomalies to do good. :D +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
